{"tid":485743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宅男應約開房　不知對方男定女 稱中伏遭cosplay戰士圍毆逼遊街","createTime":"2017-12-01T08:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T07:56:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"45adeef87a50d3e76849d2686f5759cd3e1c9830","tid":485743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171201/20231035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F20231035&d=R5uB2q%2F6rUkR92WZqqw0yZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=92a51ea2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F20231035&h=39928a1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171201/20231035</a><br />\n<br />\n宅男應約開房　不知對方男定女<br />\n稱中伏遭cosplay戰士圍毆逼遊街<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】少年動漫迷遭女網友「請食檸檬」拒絕約會後，在網上大肆羞辱她們。有人疑用「女神計」復仇，約他在去年情人節開房，實際早有埋伏圍毆他，嘲笑他「傻仔」兼逼他拍片向所有女動漫迷道歉。涉參與計劃的4男1女昨受審，動漫迷出庭憶述，事件源於一個陌生人WhatsApp約他：「聽日得唔得閒同我開房？」他爽快答應。主控質疑兩人素未謀面，怎知對方是男是女？動漫迷答「我梗係想係女仔啦」。<br />\n<br />\n記者︰歐陽聯發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171201/large/a1401a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171201%2Flarge%2Fa1401a.gif&h=342074f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主羅浩峰疑在網上唱衰女coser後遭報復欺凌。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n事主羅浩峰案發時只有17歲，現年19歲的他昨由家人陪着到庭，羅供稱無業，但即改口「係待業」。羅說話語速快，法官多次提醒他咬字要清晰，「唔好對住張枱講」。羅說到關鍵圍毆案情，不停把玩手上的身份證，又再口齒不清，法官不禁責備他：「你可唔可以專心啲？」<br />\n<br />\n羅稱案發凌晨收到第二個訊息，發訊人頭像是一個女生，他不認識對方，但既然對方想約會，於是應約。他憑相認出孤身一人的女被告「虎牙」，他形容對方身材似小學生，他昨扮女聲模仿對方當時哄他：「我哋行街後去酒店book房」。他跟女方到九展後樓梯，忽然「白毛」、「未來戰士」及「皮褸男」從梯間冒出，他稱不認識他們。他指稱眾人恐嚇要打他，挾持他到九龍灣零碳天地公園。突然羅稱漏說一件「好重要嘅事」，就是「虎牙」在梯間當面嘲笑他：「乜你覺得呢個世界有真嘅愛情咩，我呃你咋儍仔」。靜了半晌，他向法官解釋「即係欺騙我出嚟呀」。法官林偉權叫他不要加個人意見，羅無奈地「嗯」了一聲，林官叫他不要「嗯」，若明白便要說出聲。<br />\n<br />\n他續作供，指到公園後「肥仔」及「玲瓏」加入欺凌。6名被告中，有人掌摑、拳打腳踢、又用一把動漫道具木刀斬他，逼他拍片向全港「女coser」道歉，全程歷時約一小時。眾人意猶未盡，押他返九展遊街示眾，逐層向遇見的每一名女coser道歉，及承認自己曾性騷擾他人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171201/large/a1401b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171201%2Flarge%2Fa1401b.gif&h=baaf7315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被口水捽面始獲釋<br />\n<br />\n在押返九展途中，途徑人流較多的天穚，羅見眾被告稍有鬆懈遂拚命逃跑，以為成功逃脫，但「跑咗300米，喘晒氣」，背後有人以「9秒9」速度追及，他欲呼救但「冇氣叫唔到」，最終連身形較胖的「肥仔」也追上，眾被告發洩怒毆他。他因不願捱打沒再逃，欲快快道歉了事，有被告見「任務完成」提議放行，惟他反覆追問「係咪真係走得，阿媽打畀我喇，天黑喇都差唔多」，他指「未來戰士」可能嫌他太煩，大罵「食屎啦你，死儍仔」，在他頭上吐口水並捽勻。最後白毛、虎牙、皮褸男還嫌教訓不夠，帶他到尖沙嘴毆打半小時後終放他走，並警告「唔好俾我喺街度見到你，如果唔係打鑊你。」<br />\n<br />\n案中被告邵頌然（18歲）、溫穎賢（29歲）、曾栢豪（24歲）、趙文俊（32歲）及蔡周慧妍（17歲），同被控襲擊、偷竊、非法禁錮和襲擊事主。負責拍片的陳顯華（18歲）早前已承罪。聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC418/17<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t為陌生被告作名「白毛」「未來戰士」<br />\n港聞 9小時前"},{"pid":"ffebfde8b9d543ee204a4c192250e429316907c3","tid":485743,"uid":51435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd示意圖"},{"pid":"13697f4fe9d3dad6338b06113e6008373772e62a","tid":485743,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 劇情精彩"},{"pid":"03e758746a21d9f64a8779658aa7a16cd39c7c29","tid":485743,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"近期最爆既笑料"},{"pid":"c8f2ce408b6dd954b9a1e23a8b3896cc241b13a3","tid":485743,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"蔡周慧妍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c16422a546fec8a1248741141cea731b87a79e","tid":485743,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蔡周慧妍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<br />\n17歲就嫁左?"},{"pid":"736aa43d22faaec9dc7baafe436920e951836485","tid":485743,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171201/large/a1401b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171201%2Flarge%2Fa1401b.gif&h=f6c5dd46&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n潛力圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇SEED? 打死你個仆街仔"},{"pid":"0d077bc3c0a12b31db024e6b6cc7348ca3fc14a0","tid":485743,"uid":61967,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"點解要開人全相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話晒都受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef48e4f660574f2f03bdd755bef98795fd8d3d92","tid":485743,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要開人全相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話晒都受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都同問，點解唔放被告個樣出嚟？"},{"pid":"a29783bdb327d137eea3292928b7a543eaba49ba","tid":485743,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"網名叫咩咩奈奈，用 鄙人 自稱 ，又自拍條J周圍send嘅果位戇鳩仔？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCosplayer圈十個有八個都唔正常啦 見怪不怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d3b2cad80b08d863ed212d5e09af5b8835dfce","tid":485743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解要開人全相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話晒都受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都同問，點解唔放被告個樣出嚟？</blockquote><br />\n被告個樣係第二段報導"},{"pid":"81ba01a5784d0cdfed925bdb7229413b184cea9e","tid":485743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解要開人全相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話晒都受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都同問，點解唔放被告個樣出嚟？</blockquote><br />\n被告個樣係第二段報導</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171201/20231055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F20231055&d=R5uB2q%2F6rUkR92WZqqw0yZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3ce14606\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F20231055&h=b6d27fbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171201/20231055</a><br />\n為陌生被告作名「白毛」「未來戰士」<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n        <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171201/large/a1402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171201%2Flarge%2Fa1402a.gif&h=0dad4833&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網名「司徒奈奈」的男事主庭上提及部份被告時，揚言不認識他們，卻能如數家珍講出各人稱呼如「白毛」、「皮褸」及「未來戰士」等。控方質疑他為何知對方名字？羅解釋，是他為了容易分辨各人而自行命名，例如「未來戰士」是因那人戴黑超cosplay。<br />\n<br />\n形容被告「高傲」<br />\n<br />\n事主又指另一被告戴的假髮「白白哋」，故起名「白毛」，自言憑面形認出對方：「佢瓜子面，望落令人有種高傲嘅感覺。」法官林偉權聞言笑謂：「輪廓同神情係兩回事嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n事主羅浩峰在警方的認人手續中，認出全部六名被告。他昨供稱，起初收到名叫「玲瓏」的人發訊相約他開房，其後得知對方是首被告陳顯華。羅昨一度未能認出身處庭上旁聽席的首被告，其後才謂：「我搵到&hellip;&hellip;見到喇，因為佢唔係坐嗰度（犯人欄）。<br />\n<br />\n其後他收到另一個WhatsApp訊息約他外出，對方是一名女生，自稱「虎牙」。羅見面時憑相認人，對方身材似小學生，不記得身高，但隨即滿有信心補充「155cm高」，法官聞言皺眉，羅承認這只是他估計。他於警方認人手續中認出「虎牙」是第六被告蔡周慧妍，昨於庭上卻說「唔係好認得喇，相隔咁耐」；惟法庭小休後改口：「諗諗吓，開始記得番，因為休息咗十五分鐘之後，諗番就記得起嗰個人。」<br />\n羅續稱，次被告邵頌然是「白毛」，因邵當時有假髮遮掩故認不到他的髮型，但憑輪廓認出他。第三被告溫穎賢是「未來戰士」，不過因他戴黑超故未能辨認對方眼睛，只能靠耳口鼻及膚色認人。第五被告趙文俊是「皮褸」，因案發時他穿皮褸。<br />\n羅又謂第四被告曾栢豪「睇落好大隻」，所以稱他做「肥仔」。<br />\n<br />\n控方按常規對羅說：「以後你講到佢，就稱呼佢做第四被告。」惟林官反對：「證人又唔係律師，佢一路叫開肥仔，咪繼續叫肥仔囉。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者楊家樂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t宅男應約開房　不知對方男定女稱中伏遭cosplay戰士圍毆逼遊街<br />\n港聞 11小時前"},{"pid":"6baab6d401b2bdbe3e08b1faf3baad5c10efa7ad","tid":485743,"uid":18167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:29:35.000Z","msg":"係咪有法律規定一論被告定係受害者<br />\n只要係男人就登得，女人就唔登得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb3b8bdcd5b008356988fba2a9fdb8924c39d97","tid":485743,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有法律規定一論被告定係受害者<br />\n只要係男人就登得，女人就唔登得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似風化案受害人身份先會保密"},{"pid":"2a4241d27b59f31e9ace0b8c476a8ee2e7ee337f","tid":485743,"uid":8766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蔡周慧妍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<br />\n17歲就嫁左?</blockquote><br />\n17歲嫁人仲要跟人地姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492ab24880543164083256cbd677ba37eeb888c3","tid":485743,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:50:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>波動撚屌</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-s